{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469500/extras/jik-ezgif.com-resize.gif?t=1738948314\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Golden Knight</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Unleash the hero within and restore peace to the kingdom of Valerond</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>About the game:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In <strong>Golden Knight</strong>, you embark on an epic journey to defeat the forces of darkness that have taken over the kingdom of Valerond. As the legendary hero Golden Knight, a defender of endangered kingdoms, you were caught off guard by the encroaching darkness while traveling through the region. Determined to save the kingdom, you venture through mysterious forests and treacherous castles, facing hordes of enemies and deadly challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This <strong>mini metroidvania RPG platformer</strong> offers an immersive experience where exploration, combat, and progression are key to victory. With high-quality 2D pixel art graphics, each environment and enemy comes to life in stunning detail as you explore the world and seek a way to restore peace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469500/extras/heineken_background-new-ezgif.com-resize.gif?t=1738948314\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Key features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Exploration and Action:</strong> Travel through dark forests and sinister castles, facing unique challenges as you explore to find treasures and essential resources for your journey.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Upgrades and Progression:</strong> Collect coins, discover campsites, and improve your abilities, such as attack and health, to become stronger as you advance. Prepare to face increasingly powerful enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dynamic Combat:</strong> Unleash your combat power with your sword, jump to avoid enemies or traps, and use your dash to dodge or hit enemies at long range.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Challenging Enemies and Bosses:</strong> Encounter a variety of enemies like slimes, skeletons, zombies, and bats. Get ready to confront terrifying bosses, including the Demon Bat, a giant evil eye, and the powerful Dark Mage.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Deadly Traps:</strong> Beware of traps scattered along the way, such as spikes, darts, and scythes, which require skill and precision to overcome.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Immersive Music:</strong> The soundtrack, inspired by classic medieval music, creates an epic and immersive atmosphere, enhancing the gameplay experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469500/extras/heineken_worldmap-ezgif.com-overlay.gif?t=1738948314\" /></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Additional features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Linear and Focused Gameplay:</strong> Complete levels, defeat bosses, and progress through the world of Valerond to restore peace and defeat the forces of evil.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Single-Player Mode:</strong> An intense, player-focused experience, ideal for those who love action and exploration challenges.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Prepare for battle!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you're ready to embark on an epic journey of action, exploration, and heroism, then <strong>Golden Knight</strong> is the game you've been waiting for. Unleash the hero within, face the darkness, and restore the glory of the kingdom of Valerond!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/34